the second half of the show

15:52.143 --> 15:54.944
-if we hurry.
-(sighs) Fine. Fine!

15:54.955 --> 15:57.363
Just give me some space,
Wonder<i> Wormon.</i>

15:57.440 --> 15:58.906
Okay, okay.

15:58.983 --> 16:01.242
That's a girl.

16:01.318 --> 16:03.119
Now we're all gonna go to the
symphony and have a good time

16:03.129 --> 16:05.037
and soak it up into our brains.
Right?

16:05.114 --> 16:06.464
You know, you're right.
It'll be fun.

16:06.541 --> 16:08.374
And maybe pinworms
aren't so bad.

16:08.451 --> 16:10.251
I mean, they're probably
more scared of our butts

16:10.327 --> 16:12.128
