worms, they're butterflies.

16:36.645 --> 16:38.320
It-it... I don't know,
it's just my process.

16:38.331 --> 16:39.497
Butt-er-flies.

16:39.574 --> 16:40.573
Oh, yeah, I didn't even
think of that.

16:40.649 --> 16:42.450
Uh, Linda, I have to say,

16:42.526 --> 16:44.910
