17:17.686 --> 17:19.695
Kids, shush.
Linda, are you okay?

17:19.706 --> 17:21.363
Linda? Lin?

17:21.374 --> 17:24.208
Oh, my God,
the slide's dead<i> and</i> Mom's dead?

17:24.285 --> 17:25.659
